WEBVTT

00:30.190 --> 00:30.960
Chun'er.

00:31.960 --> 00:33.420
I was betrayed by Huan Huan

00:33.710 --> 00:35.640
and have lost control of Great Yan.

00:36.390 --> 00:37.960
I hope you can help me

00:38.710 --> 00:39.840
take back Great Yan.

00:42.710 --> 00:44.200
Why should I help you?

00:44.840 --> 00:47.600
You are nothing but an abandoned pawn now.

01:15.840 --> 01:16.870
No matter what you think,

01:16.870 --> 01:17.930
I will give it a try.

01:18.710 --> 01:19.920
I can do anything,

01:20.430 --> 01:22.070
even if it means risking my life.

01:22.070 --> 01:23.310
Just please help me.

01:26.120 --> 01:27.780
You've already dirtied this.

01:28.430 --> 01:29.760
I don't want it anymore.

01:31.760 --> 01:34.490
I am now
a mighty Princess Protector of the State.

01:34.640 --> 01:35.920
If you want to see me,

01:36.310 --> 01:39.370
come to the Princess's Mansion
to request an audience.

03:14.060 --> 03:19.440
[REBIRTH]

03:20.079 --> 03:22.430
[Episode 35]

03:22.490 --> 03:26.000
[Princess's Mansion]

03:32.750 --> 03:34.120
Our Princess said

03:34.470 --> 03:35.800
if you wanted to see her,

03:36.079 --> 03:38.150
you must kneel here for 24 hours

03:38.360 --> 03:40.020
to have the honor of entering.

03:48.630 --> 03:50.430
Our Princess also said

03:50.840 --> 03:52.120
she was just...

03:52.590 --> 03:53.720
trying to scare you.

03:54.400 --> 03:56.000
-To scare you.
-To scare you.

03:56.400 --> 03:57.530
She gave you 4 hours.

03:57.590 --> 03:58.390
-Four.
-Four.

03:58.750 --> 03:59.560
Follow me.

04:04.590 --> 04:05.560
Yan Xun.

04:06.710 --> 04:07.630
Do you know?

04:08.400 --> 04:10.360
I used to really like you.

04:11.680 --> 04:13.190
But you ruined me.

04:16.560 --> 04:19.160
I have no feelings for you now.

04:20.720 --> 04:22.160
Why should I help you?

04:25.360 --> 04:26.040
Chun'er.

04:27.870 --> 04:29.070
I am powerless now.

04:29.830 --> 04:31.830
The future of Great Yan is in danger.

04:32.190 --> 04:34.050
If you can give me 5,000 soldiers,

04:34.830 --> 04:36.510
I can take back Great Yan.

04:37.360 --> 04:38.820
As long as you are willing,

04:39.870 --> 04:41.870
I am willing to atone for everything

04:42.560 --> 04:43.270
in the past.

04:48.240 --> 04:49.000
Is that so?

04:56.870 --> 04:59.330
Are you really willing
to do anything for me?

05:00.160 --> 05:01.120
I am.

05:07.310 --> 05:08.840
Change into these clothes.

05:14.920 --> 05:15.510
Wait.

05:16.520 --> 05:17.590
Change right here.

06:17.240 --> 06:18.160
Li Yan.

06:19.160 --> 06:19.800
Chun'er.

06:20.630 --> 06:21.750
I miss you so much.

06:37.750 --> 06:38.480
Li Yan.

08:23.600 --> 08:24.310
No.

08:24.720 --> 08:27.520
These eyebrows don't look like
he drew them at all!

08:29.000 --> 08:29.630
Chun'er.

08:31.310 --> 08:32.000
Chun'er.

08:47.240 --> 08:47.960
Chun'er!

08:48.390 --> 08:49.120
Chun'er!

08:50.160 --> 08:53.780
♪ The dust in the world ♪

08:50.480 --> 08:51.240
Chun'er.

08:52.600 --> 08:53.390
Why?

08:54.300 --> 08:57.770
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

08:54.550 --> 08:56.630
Why do you treat me like this?

08:56.630 --> 08:57.360
Chun'er.

08:58.360 --> 08:59.550
Why didn't you tell me

08:58.480 --> 09:01.280
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

08:59.550 --> 09:00.870
that you are the Empress's son?

09:00.870 --> 09:03.200
Why did you leave me to die alone?

09:02.110 --> 09:03.460
♪ And not be scared? ♪

09:03.480 --> 09:05.500
♪ A slight ripple ♪

09:03.790 --> 09:05.600
Do you know that I hate you?

09:05.670 --> 09:07.080
I hate you!

09:05.680 --> 09:09.270
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

09:07.120 --> 09:08.080
-Chun'er!
-I hate you!

09:08.080 --> 09:08.670
I hate you!

09:08.670 --> 09:09.320
Chun'er!

09:09.320 --> 09:10.270
I hate you!

09:09.550 --> 09:12.920
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

09:10.390 --> 09:11.200
Chun'er!

09:11.200 --> 09:11.840
Chun'er!

09:12.910 --> 09:13.550
Chun'er.

09:13.890 --> 09:16.740
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

09:17.400 --> 09:20.770
♪ Let it be ♪

09:20.200 --> 09:21.850
You are a favored daughter of heaven,

09:21.850 --> 09:25.280
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

09:22.960 --> 09:24.480
a noble Princess.

09:24.790 --> 09:26.600
You shouldn't have been involved
in this conflict.

09:25.760 --> 09:28.770
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

09:27.270 --> 09:29.870
I didn't tell you
because I wanted to protect you.

09:29.150 --> 09:30.780
♪ Go weaving ♪

09:31.110 --> 09:36.060
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

09:31.480 --> 09:32.720
I wanted you

09:34.150 --> 09:35.280
to live a life of joy,

09:36.780 --> 09:39.330
♪ We face ♪

09:36.910 --> 09:38.710
contentment, and good fortune.

09:39.350 --> 09:43.210
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

09:44.360 --> 09:47.090
♪ Even with extreme pain ♪

09:47.120 --> 09:51.890
♪ We don't even wince ♪

09:52.150 --> 09:52.670
I...

09:52.310 --> 09:55.160
♪ Why in this world ♪

09:53.840 --> 09:54.870
didn't get to...

09:55.180 --> 09:59.670
♪ The staunchest heart
and strongest soul ♪

09:57.000 --> 09:58.080
tell you...

09:59.240 --> 10:00.390
anything at all.

10:07.080 --> 10:07.840
Chun'er.

10:09.790 --> 10:10.390
I'm here.

10:11.440 --> 10:12.510
I didn't get to...

10:15.240 --> 10:16.840
didn't get to...

11:14.150 --> 11:15.120
Guards!

11:19.670 --> 11:21.000
Chun'er, you're awake.

11:21.150 --> 11:24.010
I specifically had someone
prepare Dew Lotus Soup.

11:26.390 --> 11:28.120
I remember it's your favorite.

11:28.360 --> 11:29.620
On summer afternoons,

11:30.870 --> 11:32.130
you always have a bowl.

11:59.600 --> 12:00.720
Hear my orders!

12:01.440 --> 12:03.240
This witch is named Chu Qiao.

12:03.480 --> 12:05.150
She is a criminal slave of Great Yong.

12:05.150 --> 12:07.240
She impersonated the Faceless Saintess

12:07.240 --> 12:08.910
and rebelled against Great Yong.

12:08.910 --> 12:12.960
Today, in front of the Jiuyou Platform
at Jinsheng Palace,

12:13.310 --> 12:15.770
she will be burned alive
as a public warning!

12:23.670 --> 12:24.600
Yan Xun.

12:25.150 --> 12:26.000
As I told you,

12:26.510 --> 12:28.710
this place holds too many bad memories.

12:29.440 --> 12:31.500
It would be better if you didn't come.

12:31.550 --> 12:32.550
But you wouldn't listen

12:32.550 --> 12:33.880
and insisted on coming.

12:39.030 --> 12:39.870
Rest assured,

12:40.600 --> 12:42.080
didn't you want my help?

12:44.030 --> 12:46.790
I've already informed
His Highness the Thirteenth.

12:46.790 --> 12:48.000
Once Chu Qiao is dead,

12:48.440 --> 12:49.910
we will lend you a troop

12:49.910 --> 12:51.910
of Zhenhuangcheng's imperial guards

12:51.910 --> 12:53.640
to help you take back Great Yan.

12:54.000 --> 12:55.660
Thank you, Princess Chun'er,

12:56.150 --> 12:58.010
and His Highness the Thirteenth.

13:38.600 --> 13:39.550
Yan Xun,

13:40.510 --> 13:41.440
you lied to me.

13:42.150 --> 13:43.000
You came to me,

13:45.080 --> 13:46.480
not to borrow troops.

13:50.870 --> 13:51.600
Speak.

13:52.080 --> 13:53.610
Where is Chu Qiao locked up?

13:55.320 --> 13:56.670
I don't know.

14:00.080 --> 14:03.410
She's been locked in the doghouse
of the Thirteenth Prince.

14:34.480 --> 14:36.940
The antidote for muscle-softening powder.

14:56.480 --> 14:57.540
My name is Chu Qiao.

14:58.790 --> 15:00.600
I was once a slave in Great Yong,

15:01.080 --> 15:03.600
and now I am the Queen of Ximeng.

15:04.240 --> 15:05.510
I know this Chu Qiao.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.970
She used to be a slave in Qingshan Manor

15:08.510 --> 15:10.510
and later defected from Great Yong.

15:13.630 --> 15:15.160
Zhao Chun'er and Zhao Yang,

15:15.550 --> 15:17.480
together with the witch, Jia Meng,

15:17.510 --> 15:20.640
used the Faceless God Sect
to oppress the common people.

15:20.750 --> 15:22.270
All their actions

15:22.270 --> 15:24.000
were aimed at annexing Ximeng.

15:24.510 --> 15:26.000
Is this true?

15:26.150 --> 15:27.480
How could such a thing happen?

15:27.480 --> 15:28.720
The current Ximeng

15:29.080 --> 15:30.720
is a brand new world.

15:30.840 --> 15:32.270
No one is a slave there,

15:32.600 --> 15:34.120
and no one can recklessly trample on

15:34.120 --> 15:35.750
the lives and dignity of others there.

15:35.750 --> 15:36.720
Every commoner

15:36.720 --> 15:38.750
can live fairly in this world.

15:39.000 --> 15:42.030
Such Ximeng will not
be dependent on Great Yong,

15:42.030 --> 15:44.430
nor will it ever associate
with Great Yong!

15:45.870 --> 15:47.600
Ximeng has abolished slavery?

15:47.750 --> 15:49.200
You don't know yet, do you?

15:49.200 --> 15:50.840
I heard that many slaves
from our Great Yong

15:50.840 --> 15:51.970
have fled to Ximeng.

15:52.600 --> 15:53.730
These past few days,

15:54.390 --> 15:55.920
by giving me the rabbit tail

15:56.630 --> 15:58.030
and feeding me the lotus soup,

15:58.030 --> 15:59.290
you treated me so well.

16:00.080 --> 16:02.000
Was it all for today's plan?

16:03.750 --> 16:05.120
This Jiuyou Platform

16:07.180 --> 16:09.310
has claimed 16 souls of the Yan family.

16:10.080 --> 16:11.600
Chu is the last important person to me

16:11.600 --> 16:12.960
in this world.

16:14.720 --> 16:16.600
I will never let her suffer

16:17.720 --> 16:19.790
the slightest harm here.

16:28.480 --> 16:29.200
Yan Xun.

16:30.600 --> 16:31.550
Have you

16:33.960 --> 16:35.840
never regretted it?

16:41.480 --> 16:42.600
Just kill me.

16:43.440 --> 16:45.900
The father of my child
has been killed by you,

16:45.910 --> 16:48.040
and my mother also died because of you.

16:48.550 --> 16:49.750
In this world,

16:50.030 --> 16:51.240
I have nothing left.

16:53.360 --> 16:55.820
Why don't you end my life
with your own hands?

16:56.240 --> 16:58.840
This way, I will no longer have any pain

16:59.910 --> 17:01.320
or attachments.

17:18.720 --> 17:19.400
Chun'er.

17:20.069 --> 17:20.750
Chun'er.

17:21.349 --> 17:22.000
Chun'er.

17:23.480 --> 17:24.160
Chun'er.

17:28.830 --> 17:29.790
Yan Xun.

17:31.550 --> 17:32.350
Chun'er.

17:34.160 --> 17:34.750
Chun'er.

17:36.240 --> 17:38.070
All these things
were done by Zhao Chun'er,

17:38.070 --> 17:40.310
including bringing in
the Faceless God Sect.

17:40.310 --> 17:41.970
Now that the murderer is dead,

17:42.440 --> 17:43.400
can I go?

17:46.720 --> 17:47.830
Can't I go?

17:48.200 --> 17:49.070
Shut up.

18:05.960 --> 18:07.560
Quickly, save the Princess!

18:25.510 --> 18:27.830
Holding a prince hostage is a great crime.

18:27.830 --> 18:29.070
If there is any misunderstanding

18:29.070 --> 18:31.330
among Ximeng, Great Yan, and Great Yong,

18:31.880 --> 18:34.210
we can put down our weapons
and talk it out.

18:34.550 --> 18:36.200
But if you persist in resisting,

18:36.200 --> 18:38.730
that would mean
making an enemy of Great Yong.

18:38.790 --> 18:39.510
Chu.

18:40.720 --> 18:41.850
Don't believe them.

18:42.030 --> 18:44.750
That's how they deceived
the Yan family back then.

18:44.750 --> 18:45.950
If we let Zhao Yang go,

18:46.510 --> 18:47.960
we will still die.

18:48.350 --> 18:49.790
Qingshan Manor, hear my orders!

18:49.790 --> 18:53.190
Capture the King of Great Yan
and Chu Qiao with all your might!

18:54.280 --> 18:55.130
Who dares!

18:56.550 --> 18:57.400
Zhuge Yue,

18:57.750 --> 18:58.810
cooperate with me.

18:59.160 --> 19:00.890
Let's get out of here together.

19:07.920 --> 19:08.790
Zhuge Yue.

19:10.000 --> 19:11.510
I gave you a choice once.

19:12.350 --> 19:13.950
I wanted you to leave with me.

19:14.240 --> 19:16.110
You gave up that path yourself.

19:16.750 --> 19:17.510
Now,

19:18.000 --> 19:21.110
I am Zhuge Yue, Chief of Qingshan Manor.

19:21.550 --> 19:22.400
You're lying.

19:23.920 --> 19:24.960
You only came back to Qingshan Manor

19:24.960 --> 19:26.160
to save me.

19:26.720 --> 19:27.480
Zhuge Yue,

19:28.400 --> 19:29.460
let's go together.

19:32.430 --> 19:33.230
You're wrong.

19:34.200 --> 19:35.200
Even without you,

19:35.680 --> 19:36.400
the blood of the Zhuge family

19:36.400 --> 19:38.070
still flows in my veins.

19:38.590 --> 19:41.720
I'm destined to belong to
Qingshan Manor for all my life.

19:41.720 --> 19:43.250
There should be a clear line

19:43.400 --> 19:45.240
between you and me.

19:57.880 --> 19:58.640
Zhuge Yue,

20:00.160 --> 20:01.960
this is not what you truly think.

20:02.790 --> 20:04.200
What you truly think

20:04.680 --> 20:06.310
is that as a member of the Zhuge family,

20:06.310 --> 20:08.070
you don't want to become like them.

20:08.070 --> 20:10.200
You never lived freely or comfortably

20:10.200 --> 20:12.200
because every moment in Qingshan Manor

20:12.200 --> 20:14.350
brought you pain and contempt!

20:14.640 --> 20:16.070
Do you think you know me that well?

20:16.070 --> 20:17.070
I know you,

20:17.270 --> 20:17.960
Zhuge Yue.

20:18.440 --> 20:20.480
I know you just as well as you know me.

20:20.480 --> 20:21.160
Well then,

20:22.240 --> 20:23.510
I'll tell you now.

20:24.510 --> 20:26.480
However many blood debts
Qingshan Manor bears,

20:26.480 --> 20:27.720
I bear them too.

20:28.240 --> 20:29.720
In Yan Shicheng's case,

20:30.030 --> 20:32.550
I was the one who handed the evidence

20:32.550 --> 20:34.350
of his rebellion to His Majesty.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.510
I knew it was fake,

20:36.790 --> 20:37.720
and I knew what price the Yan family

20:37.720 --> 20:39.680
would pay for it.

20:44.680 --> 20:45.880
You don't believe me?

20:48.070 --> 20:48.960
Then ask him.

20:51.440 --> 20:52.070
Yan Xun,

20:54.200 --> 20:55.730
is everything he said true?

20:56.030 --> 20:57.920
Why did you never tell me?

20:58.590 --> 21:01.310
Because I thought
he still had a shred of conscience.

21:01.310 --> 21:03.110
I thought leaving you in my care

21:03.310 --> 21:05.040
was truly a temporary measure.

21:05.590 --> 21:07.440
But I didn't expect him to still choose

21:07.440 --> 21:08.500
his Qingshan Manor

21:09.160 --> 21:10.440
and the Zhuge family.

21:16.720 --> 21:18.000
Do you really think

21:19.240 --> 21:21.440
you can help me escape the Zhuge family?

21:22.550 --> 21:23.350
Ridiculous.

21:24.680 --> 21:26.310
Abolishing slavery and stopping wars?

21:26.310 --> 21:27.790
Justice and freedom?

21:28.350 --> 21:29.880
Open your eyes and see

21:30.440 --> 21:31.960
who you really helped.

21:33.070 --> 21:35.880
If you hadn't implemented
new policies in Ximeng,

21:36.240 --> 21:37.400
Great Yong would never have had

21:37.400 --> 21:39.960
the slightest interest
in such a barren land.

21:40.720 --> 21:43.790
You thought you were helping
Yan Xun escape Zhenhuangcheng.

21:43.790 --> 21:45.160
Now take a good look.

21:45.830 --> 21:46.790
After all this,

21:47.550 --> 21:49.480
hasn't he ended up right back here?

21:51.240 --> 21:52.000
Yan Xun,

21:52.880 --> 21:54.680
you are the new King of Great Yan.

21:55.070 --> 21:57.680
Are you really willing to give up

21:57.750 --> 22:00.810
the people of Great Yan
and your throne for a slave girl?

22:49.030 --> 22:50.960
Chu Qiao, a criminal slave of Great Yong,

22:50.960 --> 22:52.720
has conspired with Yan Xun,
King of Great Yan,

22:52.720 --> 22:54.320
to rebel against Great Yong.

22:54.510 --> 22:55.680
Qingshan Manor, listen to my command!

22:55.680 --> 22:56.350
-Here!
-Here!

22:56.350 --> 22:57.510
Arrest them both!

22:57.830 --> 22:58.490
-Yes!
-Yes!

22:58.680 --> 22:59.350
Wait!

23:07.480 --> 23:08.480
His Majesty has an order.

23:08.480 --> 23:10.200
Release Empress Dowager Xiuli of Biantang

23:10.200 --> 23:12.660
and King of Great Yan,
Yan Xun, immediately.

23:29.480 --> 23:30.610
Young Master Zhuge,

23:31.590 --> 23:34.190
do you just let them go
without doing anything?

23:34.350 --> 23:36.210
They attempted to assassinate me

23:36.350 --> 23:37.480
and Father.

23:38.090 --> 23:39.690
This is His Majesty's order.

23:41.070 --> 23:42.670
Don't use Father to scare me!

23:42.960 --> 23:45.960
They deserve to die
for attempting to assassinate me!

23:48.480 --> 23:49.200
Your Highness the Thirteenth Prince,

23:49.200 --> 23:50.200
Biantang sent envoys

23:50.200 --> 23:51.510
to ask His Majesty to release them.

23:51.510 --> 23:53.510
Please consider the big picture,

23:53.620 --> 23:55.750
and do not disobey His Majesty's will.

24:05.830 --> 24:07.510
Fire! Fire!

24:07.790 --> 24:10.720
An ominous sign! An ominous sign!

24:32.880 --> 24:35.080
This is the Faceless God's punishment!

24:35.310 --> 24:38.240
The Thirteenth Prince
has angered the Faceless God!

24:38.950 --> 24:41.410
Is it really
the Faceless God's punishment?

24:45.920 --> 24:46.780
Pass my orders.

24:47.310 --> 24:50.370
Qingshan Manor spies
and imperial guard will split up.

24:50.480 --> 24:52.200
One team to close the city gates
and put out the fire,

24:52.200 --> 24:54.310
and the other to protect the civilians.

24:54.310 --> 24:54.970
-Yes!
-Yes!

24:56.480 --> 24:59.000
-Come, put out the fire!
-Come, put out the fire!

24:59.000 --> 25:00.270
-Over here!
-Over here!

25:00.270 --> 25:00.790
Hurry!

25:05.920 --> 25:06.750
Yang.

25:07.640 --> 25:09.960
My Yang.

25:12.940 --> 25:15.550
My Yang.

25:19.880 --> 25:21.070
Yang.

25:24.240 --> 25:26.270
My Yang.

25:30.590 --> 25:32.030
Yang.

25:33.310 --> 25:34.510
Your Majesty,

25:34.790 --> 25:36.720
the Thirteenth Prince was murdered

25:36.720 --> 25:39.070
by poison.

25:43.790 --> 25:44.790
Why?

25:48.680 --> 25:50.200
Why?

25:54.110 --> 25:55.240
Zhao Che,

25:56.720 --> 26:00.000
I know you've always coveted the throne

26:00.480 --> 26:02.790
and seen Yang as a thorn in your side,

26:02.790 --> 26:03.990
a thorn in your flesh.

26:09.000 --> 26:12.200
Do you think I don't know

26:12.400 --> 26:14.200
what you're planning?

26:14.790 --> 26:16.110
You have talent,

26:16.400 --> 26:17.730
and you have a strategy.

26:19.030 --> 26:22.350
You also have wild ambitions.

26:24.400 --> 26:26.350
Wild ambitions.

26:27.160 --> 26:27.960
That's right.

26:28.750 --> 26:30.480
I killed Zhao Yang.

26:31.240 --> 26:32.110
Father.

26:33.680 --> 26:36.000
Is this the path I wanted to take?

26:39.880 --> 26:41.790
I entered the army at 13.

26:42.640 --> 26:44.170
I lived a life of bloodshed.

26:44.350 --> 26:46.610
Ten years of life and death on the border—

26:47.110 --> 26:49.370
I never harbored any disloyal thoughts.

26:50.310 --> 26:51.310
But you, Father,

26:52.270 --> 26:53.640
you don't trust me,

26:54.270 --> 26:55.600
testing me at every step

26:55.880 --> 26:57.480
and suspecting me every day.

26:58.830 --> 27:01.290
No matter how hard I try
or how loyal I remain,

27:01.440 --> 27:03.840
I'm only labeled as wildly ambitious.

27:04.830 --> 27:06.880
I only wanted to defend this country

27:06.880 --> 27:07.960
and protect its people.

27:07.960 --> 27:08.830
But Father,

27:09.000 --> 27:09.880
it was you.

27:09.880 --> 27:12.640
You forced me onto this path of no return!

27:17.790 --> 27:19.400
I fought bloody battles
on the battlefield,

27:19.400 --> 27:21.550
surviving 34 campaigns.

27:21.550 --> 27:23.070
A fifth of Great Yong

27:24.110 --> 27:26.480
was bought with my life!

27:29.910 --> 27:32.310
I narrowly escaped death countless times.

27:33.030 --> 27:34.030
But in the end,

27:34.400 --> 27:36.550
all I got is your wariness,

27:36.720 --> 27:37.510
and being trampled on by Zhao Yang,

27:37.510 --> 27:39.880
such an absurd and incompetent person!

27:40.820 --> 27:43.140
Yang was absurd,

27:43.560 --> 27:46.190
but he wouldn't hurt you!

27:58.310 --> 27:59.640
You are wrong, Father.

28:00.160 --> 28:01.480
What you mean is,

28:02.030 --> 28:04.310
he wouldn't hurt you, right?

28:04.760 --> 28:06.720
Because he was simple and foolish.

28:07.000 --> 28:07.960
Therefore,

28:09.070 --> 28:10.590
relying heavily on him

28:10.960 --> 28:12.830
makes you feel much safer
than relying on a capable

28:12.830 --> 28:14.880
and accomplished son.

28:15.880 --> 28:18.110
I fought bloody battles
on the battlefield,

28:18.110 --> 28:21.240
fighting through mountains of swords
and seas of blood.

28:21.240 --> 28:22.270
But Zhao Yang

28:23.310 --> 28:26.510
was indulging in debauchery
and fighting his brothers.

28:26.790 --> 28:27.680
Why should I

28:28.960 --> 28:30.680
be beneath someone like him?

28:33.640 --> 28:35.590
Today, I've rebelled,

28:37.240 --> 28:39.000
confirming your suspicions.

28:39.440 --> 28:42.310
I have become a traitor in your eyes.

28:56.550 --> 28:57.640
But Father,

28:59.240 --> 29:01.200
is everything I've done

29:02.600 --> 29:04.640
really my fault?

29:25.440 --> 29:27.550
Please write an edict

29:28.160 --> 29:29.920
to make me the Crown Prince.

30:14.000 --> 30:15.600
Here is His Majesty's edict.

30:16.270 --> 30:17.270
From now on,

30:18.240 --> 30:20.500
the Seventh Prince Zhao Che is appointed

30:22.000 --> 30:23.640
as the Crown Prince.

30:26.460 --> 30:28.390
Congratulations, Your Highness.

30:30.830 --> 30:35.360
-Paying respects to you, Your Highness.
-Paying respects to you, Your Highness.

30:36.110 --> 30:37.240
From this moment on,

30:37.680 --> 30:39.400
seal the city gates immediately.

30:39.400 --> 30:41.720
No one is allowed to leave Zhenhuangcheng.

30:41.720 --> 30:42.680
Your Highness,

30:42.920 --> 30:44.830
the envoys from Biantang
are still in the city.

30:44.830 --> 30:46.430
How should we deal with them?

30:46.720 --> 30:48.350
Execute them all.

30:48.830 --> 30:49.480
Yes.

30:50.490 --> 30:56.100
[Qingshan Manor]

30:56.510 --> 30:57.410
I promised you

30:58.200 --> 31:00.130
that if you could capture Chu Qiao,

31:00.240 --> 31:02.570
her life or death
would be yours to decide.

31:02.720 --> 31:03.640
But today,

31:04.440 --> 31:06.110
you let her and Yan Xun escape.

31:07.830 --> 31:08.920
Rest assured, Your Highness.

31:08.920 --> 31:10.960
The captains at each gate have checked

31:10.960 --> 31:13.000
that Yan Xun and Chu Qiao
haven't left the city.

31:13.000 --> 31:15.200
I won't let her interfere with our plan.

31:16.480 --> 31:18.280
If they escape back to Great Yan,

31:19.110 --> 31:20.840
they will definitely come back

31:21.070 --> 31:23.110
with the army of Great Yan
to attack us just like before

31:23.110 --> 31:26.310
and start a war among Great Yan,
Biantang, and Great Yong.

31:26.310 --> 31:27.510
When that time comes,

31:28.680 --> 31:30.940
I'm afraid I'll have to break my promise.

32:07.270 --> 32:08.240
Reporting, General,

32:08.240 --> 32:09.880
the soldiers of Great Yong
have been following us.

32:09.880 --> 32:12.480
I couldn't get any news
about Zhenhuangcheng.

32:15.160 --> 32:17.110
We came all the way via the official road.

32:17.110 --> 32:18.000
Several groups of troops

32:18.000 --> 32:20.200
were heading towards Zhenhuangcheng.

32:20.240 --> 32:23.030
Something big must have happened
in Zhenhuangcheng.

32:23.030 --> 32:24.830
I have to go back and save Yan Xun.

32:25.270 --> 32:27.240
Stay here and help me hold them off.

32:27.880 --> 32:28.400
Yes.

32:44.720 --> 32:46.120
Why is the Yong Army here?

32:46.310 --> 32:47.110
General Huan,

32:47.240 --> 32:48.500
should we go up and ask?

32:51.270 --> 32:52.070
General Huan,

32:52.350 --> 32:54.590
His Highness the Crown Prince
invites you to the palace.

32:54.590 --> 32:56.790
I have been waiting here for a long time.

32:57.070 --> 32:58.800
His Highness the Crown Prince?

32:59.160 --> 33:01.070
Since when did Great Yong
have a Crown Prince?

33:01.070 --> 33:02.350
General Huan, you might not know.

33:02.350 --> 33:04.070
His Majesty has issued an official decree,

33:04.070 --> 33:07.130
naming the Seventh Prince Zhao Che
as the Crown Prince.

33:08.160 --> 33:09.110
Zhao Che.

33:18.350 --> 33:19.950
The wound has been bandaged.

33:19.960 --> 33:21.240
We don't have medicine here.

33:21.240 --> 33:23.040
You have to endure it for a while.

33:25.790 --> 33:28.480
That day, Zhao Yang
suddenly died on the altar.

33:28.920 --> 33:31.200
Zhenhuangcheng is under martial law now.

33:31.200 --> 33:32.660
The city gates are closed.

33:33.110 --> 33:34.370
We can't leave for now.

33:36.680 --> 33:37.350
Yan Xun,

33:39.000 --> 33:40.530
did I make the wrong choice?

33:41.070 --> 33:42.110
If

33:42.640 --> 33:44.510
Zhuge Yue and I had left Ximeng,

33:45.240 --> 33:46.920
this wouldn't be happening now.

33:46.920 --> 33:47.480
Chu,

33:48.960 --> 33:49.890
you used to never

33:50.510 --> 33:53.170
speculate on things
that had already happened.

33:56.480 --> 33:57.000
Chu,

33:58.350 --> 33:59.400
before I met you,

33:59.880 --> 34:00.920
I always thought

34:01.270 --> 34:03.330
that everyone had their own destiny.

34:04.440 --> 34:05.970
Slaves have their destiny,

34:06.550 --> 34:08.150
heir apparents have theirs,

34:08.440 --> 34:10.239
and princesses have theirs too.

34:12.110 --> 34:13.800
But who made these rules?

34:14.360 --> 34:15.889
I never thought about that.

34:18.110 --> 34:18.800
It was you

34:19.960 --> 34:21.800
who told me not to accept my fate

34:22.150 --> 34:23.840
during the darkest time of my life.

34:23.840 --> 34:25.550
You changed my destiny

34:26.150 --> 34:28.010
and the destinies of many others,

34:29.320 --> 34:31.120
including the people of Ximeng.

34:32.000 --> 34:33.600
You've brought a ray of light

34:34.320 --> 34:35.670
to this dark world.

34:36.360 --> 34:37.510
Even if it's faint,

34:38.920 --> 34:41.050
it's enough for many people to watch it

34:41.510 --> 34:42.440
and keep living.

36:01.070 --> 36:02.190
When I was little,

36:02.760 --> 36:03.890
at every sacrifice,

36:05.110 --> 36:07.320
I stood at the very back.

36:22.670 --> 36:25.190
I always dreamed of getting closer

36:26.400 --> 36:28.000
to take a close look

36:28.440 --> 36:30.670
at the portraits and memorial tablets

36:31.230 --> 36:32.960
of the ancestors of Great Yong.

36:34.960 --> 36:36.000
Until today,

36:38.110 --> 36:39.630
I can get so close

36:41.360 --> 36:43.290
and see clearly for the first time.

36:52.710 --> 36:53.310
Huan Huan.

36:54.440 --> 36:56.100
We have similar backgrounds.

36:57.360 --> 37:00.400
Neither of us had the protection
of parents since childhood.

37:00.400 --> 37:02.660
We had to fight for everything on our own.

37:03.360 --> 37:05.020
You surely can understand me.

37:07.630 --> 37:08.510
I know.

37:09.440 --> 37:11.100
Without parents' protection

37:11.320 --> 37:13.110
and relying on yourself all the way,

37:13.110 --> 37:14.970
it must have been extremely hard.

37:28.510 --> 37:29.190
Huan Huan.

37:30.760 --> 37:33.090
I've spent half my life on the battlefield

37:34.110 --> 37:36.110
and never been attracted to a woman,

37:36.510 --> 37:37.760
until I met you.

37:46.280 --> 37:47.480
If you are willing

37:48.110 --> 37:50.240
to represent the 13 tribes of Great Yan

37:50.360 --> 37:52.290
and not make an enemy of Great Yong,

37:52.440 --> 37:53.770
Great Yong and Great Yan

37:54.800 --> 37:56.630
will cease fire forever.

37:57.590 --> 37:58.990
Then the past grievances

37:59.440 --> 38:01.070
can also be written off.

38:04.880 --> 38:05.630
But...

38:14.360 --> 38:15.070
Huan Huan.

38:16.110 --> 38:18.440
I'm not someone who loves killing and war.

38:19.400 --> 38:21.110
I hope Great Yong and Great Yan

38:22.710 --> 38:24.150
can live in peace.

38:24.880 --> 38:27.110
I hope even more to stand with you.

38:54.920 --> 38:55.550
Huan Huan.

38:57.110 --> 39:00.240
I will definitely become
the master of Zhenhuangcheng.

39:10.070 --> 39:10.800
What is this?

39:11.000 --> 39:13.530
This is an item
of the Great Yong royal family.

39:13.920 --> 39:15.150
Each prince has one,

39:15.990 --> 39:19.100
bearing his own unique pattern
and his rank.

39:19.420 --> 39:23.040
♪ The dust in the world ♪

39:23.000 --> 39:23.920
I give it to you.

39:23.560 --> 39:27.040
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

39:26.760 --> 39:29.190
Is this a love token?

39:27.740 --> 39:30.540
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

39:30.710 --> 39:32.960
This is the interest on that donkey.

39:31.380 --> 39:32.720
♪ And not be scared? ♪

39:32.750 --> 39:34.760
♪ A slight ripple ♪

39:34.950 --> 39:38.540
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

39:38.820 --> 39:42.190
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

39:43.160 --> 39:46.000
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

39:46.670 --> 39:50.040
♪ Let it be ♪

39:50.070 --> 39:51.190
Then my donkey

39:51.120 --> 39:54.550
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

39:53.630 --> 39:54.890
is too cheap, isn't it?

39:55.020 --> 39:58.040
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

39:58.420 --> 40:00.050
♪ Go weaving ♪

40:00.380 --> 40:05.330
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

40:05.630 --> 40:06.230
Huan Huan,

40:06.250 --> 40:08.800
♪ We face ♪

40:07.140 --> 40:09.020
I want to be with you like this forever.

40:08.820 --> 40:12.670
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

40:13.830 --> 40:16.560
♪ Even with extreme pain ♪

40:16.590 --> 40:21.350
♪ We don't even wince ♪

40:21.520 --> 40:24.590
♪ Why in this world ♪

40:24.620 --> 40:29.400
♪ The staunchest heart
and strongest soul ♪

40:29.670 --> 40:36.490
♪ Yield so easily to gentle warmth? ♪

40:37.090 --> 40:39.880
♪ We once beheld ♪

40:39.910 --> 40:43.310
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

40:45.030 --> 40:47.670
♪ Beauty never ♪

40:47.700 --> 40:52.430
♪ Lasts for long ♪

40:52.700 --> 40:56.220
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

40:56.240 --> 41:00.680
♪ It's just a stone ♪

41:00.970 --> 41:08.180
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

41:09.090 --> 41:20.860
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

41:34.760 --> 41:35.440
Zhao Che,

41:36.510 --> 41:37.630
I really like you.

41:39.150 --> 41:40.610
But I was born in Great Yan,

41:41.320 --> 41:43.380
destined to be one of them all my life.

41:43.960 --> 41:45.760
I can't let go of Great Yan

41:45.880 --> 41:47.010
and join Great Yong.

41:48.400 --> 41:49.660
Let's treat last night

41:50.190 --> 41:52.150
as a beautiful dream.

41:53.550 --> 41:54.610
When we meet again,

41:55.630 --> 41:57.960
you will be the Crown Prince
of Great Yong,

41:58.000 --> 42:00.330
and I can only be General Huan
of Great Yan.

42:01.150 --> 42:02.880
When we meet on the battlefield,

42:02.880 --> 42:04.540
there's no need to show mercy.

42:24.030 --> 42:25.320
You promised me before

42:25.630 --> 42:27.880
that you wouldn't let Chu Qiao
interfere with our plan.

42:27.880 --> 42:30.000
Eradicate the evil
and destroy the disrespectful!

42:30.000 --> 42:31.260
If you don't leave now,

42:31.960 --> 42:33.070
you won't be able to leave.

42:33.070 --> 42:35.320
Then thank you, Young Master Zhuge.

42:35.320 --> 42:37.400
You can't die without my order!

42:37.510 --> 42:38.630
You told me

42:38.630 --> 42:40.480
that as long as I took good care of Chu,

42:40.480 --> 42:41.670
you would come back.

42:44.030 --> 42:44.760
Huan Huan.

42:45.070 --> 42:46.920
Capture the King of Great Yan immediately.
